# Data Dictionary — arts2021

## Data source
USPTO patent claims + PatentsView — Patent claims for NLP-indicator extraction
Access: public; Provenance: USPTO

## Key variables
- Unit of analysis: patent claim
- Time window: USPTO coverage
- Sample N: unknown
- Filter rules: P1-P10 preprocessing steps

## Indicator definitions
- Formula: I1-I5 novelty (5 formulas correct); I6-I9 reuse (bug); I5/I10 cosine-similarity
- Parameters: n-gram window, cosine binary TF
- Computation steps: tokenize, n-gram extract, cosine sim
